{"tid":1764801,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【目擊高以翔出事】網傳陳偉霆寧願違約賠錢 退出浙江衛視跨年晚會","createTime":"2019-12-01T11:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T08:58:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e11c485e09f166648b10c3d27bb05d30b9db2786","tid":1764801,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T11:14:39.000Z","msg":"高以翔上月27日拍攝浙江衛視節目《追我吧》猝逝，當時陳偉霆都在現場錄影節目，並有陪同高以翔送院，可惜最後高以翔未能救回一命，陳偉霆十分傷心，一直沒有接受訪問；今日大陸網傳陳偉霆本來要參加浙江衛視跨年晚會，現在他的團隊寧願違約賠錢，也不去趟渾水云云。<br />\n<br />\n據報道指出，自從發生了高以翔事件後，粉絲紛紛指控浙江衛視隱瞞內幕，高以翔死得不明不白，現在浙江衛視內部出現動盪，很多藝人原本打算參加該台的跨年晚會，現在都紛紛退出，其中包括陳偉霆，報道並指Angelababy亦跟浙江衛視鬧僵了，不過暫時還沒退出跨年晚會。<br />\n《蘋果》向陳偉霆經理人霍汶希求證，她以短訊否認傳聞：「我們一直都沒有接浙江衛視跨年的活動呢！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191201/large/1575193851_184f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191201%2Flarge%2F1575193851_184f.jpg&h=8045088c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191201/60330998\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191201%2F60330998&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0BwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=80104dc6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191201%2F60330998&h=8a5e7826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191201/60330998</a>"},{"pid":"3c6f86d0b74e8c03766b6986a8a6146e5e4a63fe","tid":1764801,"uid":143093,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T11:15:28.000Z","msg":"見住人死咁大打擊"},{"pid":"fd8b9df7e2bc3bc3862bbd8e7729329250d1cc0f","tid":1764801,"uid":132587,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T11:17:20.000Z","msg":"點解死果個唔係佢"},{"pid":"beac826989b567a46ea24bc0c88a0ed8b65df09b","tid":1764801,"uid":51753,"like":0,"disl